'''迦薩浸信會'''是一間[[浸礼宗|浸信宗]]的[[基督教會|基督教會]]，在[[巴勒斯坦领土|巴勒斯坦]][[加沙地帶|加沙地帶]]的[[加薩|加沙市]]。<ref name="Alford 2007-10-08">{{cite news|first=Deann|last=Alford|title=Christian Bookstore Manager Martyred in Gaza City|date=2007-10-08|url=http://www.christianitytoday.com/ct/2007/octoberweb-only/141-12.0.html|work=Christianity Today|accessdate=2010-09-20|archive-date=2011-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110225033954/http://www.christianitytoday.com/ct/2007/octoberweb-only/141-12.0.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Haaretz 2007-10-07">{{cite news|title=Palestinian Christian activist stabbed to death in Gaza|date=2007-10-07|publisher=[[Haaretz|Haaretz]]|url=http://www.haaretz.com/news/palestinian-christian-activist-stabbed-to-death-in-gaza-1.230592|work=Associated Press|accessdate=2010-09-20|archive-date=2010-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100609045934/http://www.haaretz.com/news/palestinian-christian-activist-stabbed-to-death-in-gaza-1.230592|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Silver 2007-10-08">{{cite news|first=Eric|last=Silver|title=Gaza's Christian bookseller killed|date=2007-10-08|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/gazas-christian-bookseller-killed-396283.html|work=The Independent|accessdate=2010-09-20|archive-date=2019-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190421202741/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/gazas-christian-bookseller-killed-396283.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>這間教會是加沙地帶僅有的三間基督教會之一，是當地唯一的[[新教|新教]]及[[福音派|福音派]]教會。

迦薩浸信教會及其約二百名會眾，受當地[[以巴冲突|巴以衝突]]的持續暴力及混亂所害。有數名教會成員在巴勒斯坦的派系衝突中傷亡。一名教會領袖在2007年被身份不明的武裝份子殺害後，加沙政府勸喻數名教會領袖，為自身安全離開加沙。因為當地的局勢及[[以色列|以色列]]一直施加的往來限制，教會牧師及領導在外流亡，只能偶然回去。

==教會概況和活動==
這間教會在1950年代建立。<ref name="Belz 2007-05-08">{{cite journal|title=Gaza’s sturdy but small Christian population confronts Islamic militancy and the Israeli blockade|url=http://www.worldmag.com/articles/16649|last=Belz|first=Mindy|date=2007-05-08|journal=WORLD Magazine|accessdate=2010-09-20|issue=9|volume=25}}</ref>教會牧師是Hanna Massad。<ref name="Alford 2005-06-17">{{cite journal|title=Love in the Land of Enmity|url=http://www.christianitytoday.com/ct/2005/july/9.44.html|last=Alford|first=Deann|date=2005-06-17|journal=Christianity Today|accessdate=2010-09-20|issue=7|volume=49|id=|archive-date=2022-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220218120420/https://www.christianitytoday.com/ct/2005/july/9.44.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

加沙地帶的基督徒有2500人。這間教會成立至今，會眾人數在150至250之間，是加沙地帶僅有的三間基督教會之一，<ref name="Jansezian 2007-06-10">{{cite news|first=Nicole|last=Jansezian|title=Gaza’s forgotten Christians|date=2007-06-10|url=http://www.israeltoday.co.il/default.aspx?tabid=132&view=item&idx=1413|work=Israel Today Magazine|accessdate=2010-09-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100612121320/http://www.israeltoday.co.il/default.aspx?tabid=132&view=item&idx=1413|archivedate=2010-06-12}}</ref><ref name="Asharq Alawsat 2007-10-20">{{cite news|first=Mounir|last=Abu Rizk|title=Christians in Gaza: An Integral Part of Society|date=2007-10-20|url=http://www.aawsat.com/english/news.asp?section=3&id=10613|work=Asharq Alawsat|accessdate=2010-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100820200232/http://www.aawsat.com/english/news.asp?section=3|archive-date=2010-08-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>並且是加沙地帶唯一的[[福音派|福音派]]教會。當地其餘兩間教會是[[希臘正教|希臘正教]]的[[聖波斐利教堂|聖波斐利教堂]]和[[天主教|天主教]]的[[迦薩聖家堂|迦薩聖家堂]]。<ref name="Asharq Alawsat 2007-10-20" /><ref name="BBC 2005-12-21">{{cite news|title=Middle East Christians: Gaza pastor|date=2005-12-21|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/4514822.stm|work=BBC News|accessdate=2010-09-20|archive-date=2010-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100310143442/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/4514822.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2006年教會開設了加沙地帶的第一間公眾基督教圖書館。<ref name="Blake 2006-11-23">{{cite news|first=Daniel|last=Blake|title=First Christian Public Library Opens in Gaza|date=2006-11-23|url=http://www.christiantoday.com/article/first.christian.public.library.opens.in.gaza/8454.htm|work=Christianity Today|accessdate=2010-09-20|archive-date=2012-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120320124713/http://www.christiantoday.com/article/first.christian.public.library.opens.in.gaza/8454.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

教會大樓有六層高。<ref name="MNN 2007-02-07">{{cite news|title=Gaza Baptist Church seized by Fatah|date=2007-02-07|url=http://www.mnnonline.org/article/9569|work=Mission Network News|accessdate=2010-09-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110727091933/http://www.mnnonline.org/article/9569|archivedate=2011年7月27日|df=}}</ref>地下兩層是公用圖書館，有基督教和非基督教書籍。<ref name="BNL 2006-11-22">{{cite news|title=Embattled Christians In Gaza Open Library Amid Violence|date=2006-11-22|url=http://www.bosnewslife.com/2584-2584-embattled-christians-in-gaza-open-library-ami|work=BosNewsLife|accessdate=2010-09-20|archive-date=2011-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110721201814/http://www.bosnewslife.com/2584-2584-embattled-christians-in-gaza-open-library-ami|dead-url=no}}</ref>四樓用作宣教事工；五樓是宿舍，給外地到訪同工寄宿；六樓是敬拜會堂。<ref name="Blake 2006-11-23" />

加沙佔少數的基督徒，傳統上和當地佔大多數的穆斯林關係良好。<ref name="AP 2007-12-23">{{cite news|title=After murder, Gaza’s Christians keep low profile|date=2007-12-23|publisher=[[MSNBC|MSNBC]]|url=http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/22380080/|work=Associated Press|accessdate=2010-09-20|archive-date=2012-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121104072634/http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/22380080/|dead-url=no}}</ref>於2007年社會秩序大亂之前，教會開展青少年事工，開辦圖書館和數間診所。至2010年5月，教會仍然營辦一間學校，有約250名學生，當中很多是穆斯林。<ref name="Belz 2007-05-08" />

==近期歷史==

===以色列炸彈攻擊===
在2007年2月或之前，教會的公眾圖書館，在三次事件中遭人縱火破壞。<ref name="MNN 2007-02-07" />2008年12月一次以色列空襲中，教會大樓被附近炸彈爆炸損毀。<ref name="Allen 2009-01-06">{{cite news|first=Bob|last=Allen|title=Gaza Baptist Church caught in crossfire|date=2009-01-06|url=http://www.abpnews.com/content/view/3749/103/|work=Associated Baptist Press|accessdate=2010-09-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110514235544/http://www.abpnews.com/content/view/3749/103/|archivedate=2011-05-14}}</ref><ref name="Kelly 2009-01-05">{{cite news|first=Mark|last=Kelly|title=Gaza Baptist Church's building sustains damage in Israeli air strike|date=2009-01-05|url=http://www.bpnews.net/bpnews.asp?id=29605|work=Baptist Press|accessdate=2010-09-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120320033026/http://www.bpnews.net/bpnews.asp?id=29605|archivedate=2012-03-20}}</ref>

===法塔赫和哈馬斯衝突===
加沙市以低層建築為主，於是迦薩浸信會大樓不尋常的高度，使其在[[法塔赫和哈馬斯衝突|法塔赫和哈馬斯衝突]]中，多次被法塔赫和哈馬斯部隊徵用作瞭望臺。因此教會數名同工被困在雙方交火中。有一次一位教會圖書館員，在敵對勢力槍戰中被擊中。<ref name="Jansezian 2007-06-10" />另一次同類事件中，一位22歲新婚的教會公車司機被殺。<ref name='Jansezian 2007-06-10'/>教會在2007年2月被法塔赫警察搜查和短暫佔用。<ref name="Alford 2007-02-07">{{cite news|first=Deann|last=Alford|title=Fatah Police Seize Gaza Baptist Church|date=2007-02-07|url=http://www.christianitytoday.com/ct/2007/februaryweb-only/106-34.0.html|work=Christianity Today|accessdate=2010-09-20|archive-date=2021-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210507011026/https://www.christianitytoday.com/ct/2007/februaryweb-only/106-34.0.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===教會領袖被害===
2007年10月，迦薩浸信會的其中一名領袖Rami Ayyad，被身份不明的武裝份子綁架，在公開虐打後被殺。<ref name="Sudilovsky 2007-10-11">{{cite news|first=Judith|last=Sudilovsky|title=Gaza Christians express unease after killing of prominent Christian|date=2007-10-11|url=http://www.catholic.org/international/international_story.php?id=25646|work=Catholic News Service|accessdate=2010-09-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121010032606/http://www.catholic.org/international/international_story.php?id=25646|archivedate=2012-10-10}}</ref><ref name="Hendricks 2007-10-09">{{cite news|first=Shawn|last=Hendricks|title=Slain Baptist in Gaza had gentle but bold witness|date=2007-10-09|url=http://www.sbcbaptistpress.org/BPnews.asp?ID=26573|work=Baptist Press|accessdate=2010-09-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120306034400/http://www.sbcbaptistpress.org/BPnews.asp?ID=26573|archivedate=2012-03-06}}</ref><ref name="Klein 2007-10-11">{{cite news|first=Aaron|last=Klein|title=Christian Bookstore Owner Was Tortured Before His Death|date=2007-10-11|url=http://www.nysun.com/foreign/christian-bookstore-owner-was-tortured-before-his/64354/|work=The New York Sun|accessdate=2010-09-21|quote=The owner of a Christian bookstore in the Gaza Strip who was found dead this weekend was publicly beaten by Islamic gunmen accusing him of spreading Christianity, witnesses and Palestinian Arab security officials said.|archive-date=2018-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181122142507/https://www.nysun.com/foreign/christian-bookstore-owner-was-tortured-before-his/64354/|dead-url=no}}</ref> Ayyad是這代人記憶中，第一個巴勒斯坦基督徒因其信仰被殺的。<ref name='Alford 2007-10-08'/><ref name="ormestad">{{Cite news|title='I Know How to Make You a Muslim'|url=https://www.haaretz.com/1.4993232|newspaper=Haaretz|accessdate=2021-10-16|language=en|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924235818/http://www.haaretz.com/weekend/magazine/i-know-how-to-make-you-a-muslim-1.232309|dead-url=no}}</ref>他是加沙唯一的基督教書店{{link-en|The Teacher's Bookshop|The Teacher's Bookshop}}的經理。<ref name="AP 2007-12-23" /><ref name="JP 2007-10-07">{{cite news|title=Palestinian Christian activist found dead in Gaza City|date=2007-10-07|url=http://www.jpost.com/Home/Article.aspx?id=77449|work=The Jerusalem Post|accessdate=2010-09-20|archive-date=2019-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191208150918/http://www.jpost.com/Home/Article.aspx?id=77449|dead-url=no}}</ref>Ayyad遇害後，加沙政府勸喻Massad牧師遷離，以確保他一家的安全。<ref name="Belz 2007-05-08" />這宗暴力案件，令其後數個月教會平常聚會的人少了。<ref name="Weber 2008-03-10">{{cite journal|title=A dwindling Christian population battles fear and economic hardship|url=http://www.christianitytoday.com/ct/2008/april/3.14.html|last=Weber|first=Jeremy|date=2008-03-10|journal=Christianity Today|accessdate=2010-09-20|issue=4|volume=52|archive-date=2009-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090907112319/http://www.christianitytoday.com/ct/2008/april/3.14.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Smith 2008-01-29">{{cite news|first=James A. Sr.|last=Smith|title=An urgent call for prayer; Gaza Christians 'desperate'|date=2008-01-29|url=http://www.gofbw.com/news.asp?ID=8340|work=Florida Baptist Witness|accessdate=2010-09-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120307100821/http://www.gofbw.com/news.asp?ID=8340|archivedate=2012-03-07}}</ref>

===以色列的封鎖及往來限制===
Ayyad被害後，教會包括Massad牧師在內的七名領袖，遵從政府勸喻離開加沙。Massad牧師一家搬到[[約旦|約旦]]，其餘六人有五人搬到靠近[[伯利恆|伯利恆]]的[[約旦河西岸地區|西岸地區]]。此後只有Massad獲以色列當局准許回去。搬到伯利恆的五人被禁止離開該地區，因此有些人多年不能和家人見面。<ref name="Belz 2007-05-08" />

Massad稱，[[2007年起對加沙的封鎖|以色列對加沙的封鎖]]，導致了「人民中很多有無路可走和絕望的感覺……更多貧困和更多苦難。」<ref name="abp_7jun2010">{{Cite web|title=American Baptist leader says Gaza flotilla reveals need for Mideast peace|url=http://www.abpnews.com/content/view/5213/53|access-date=2021-10-16|publisher=Associated Baptist Press|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100611074119/http://www.abpnews.com/content/view/5213/53|archive-date=2010-06-11}}</ref>當地生活費用上漲，醫療儀器短缺，但是絕大多數的當地人同意，相比起來更難忍受的，是以色列施加的往來限制。Massad總結巴勒斯坦基督徒的困境，就像生存於「兩團火之間，一團是穆斯林的迫害，一團是以色列的佔領。」<ref name="Belz 2007-05-08" />

